videos.headline: Stephen Johnson runs for longest play of season for Kentucky
videos.description: Kentucky QB Stephen Johnson fools the defense and takes it 75 yards to the Tennessee 10-yard line.

videos.headline: Williams goes untouched into the end zone
videos.description: Stanley Williams run for 10-yards for a TD (Austin MacGinnis KICK)

videos.headline: Dobbs finds wide open Smith to even the score
videos.description: Tennessee's Joshua Dobbs throws it to a wide open Josh Smith in the end zone for a 24-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Dobbs takes flight on 35-yard run
videos.description: Joshua Dobbs runs for 35-yards and gets knocked out at the 1-yard line as he goes airborne. Ruling on the field stands after long review.

videos.headline: Dobbs keeper puts finishing touch on long Tennessee TD drive
videos.description: Joshua Dobbs run for 1-yard for a TD (Aaron Medley KICK)

videos.headline: Dobbs hits Wolf to extend the lead
videos.description: Joshua Dobbs pass complete to Ethan Wolf for 10-yards for a TD (Aaron Medley KICK)

videos.headline: Alvin Kamara dances through Kentucky D for big gain
videos.description: Alvin Kamara run for 39-yards to the Kent 44 for a 1ST down

videos.headline: Baity rips it away from Jennings for the pick
videos.description: Joshua Dobbs pass intercepted Derrick Baity return for no gain to the Kent 36

videos.headline: Dobbs and Malone connect on the flea flicker for the score
videos.description: Tennessee QB Joshua Dobbs connects with Josh Malone for a 51-yard touchdown in the third quarter against Kentucky.

videos.headline: Blake Bone makes athletic catch along the sideline
videos.description: Stephen Johnson pass complete to Blake Bone for 37-yards to the Tenn 14 for a 1st down. Call of no-catch reversed after review.

videos.headline: Benny Snell Jr fumble snuffs out Kentucky drive
videos.description: Benny Snell Jr. run for 4-yards to the Tenn 4 Benny Snell Jr. fumbled, forced by Stephen Griffin, recovered by Tenn LaTroy Lewis

videos.headline: Kamara rockets through the hole for paydirt
videos.description: Alvin Kamara run for 17-yards for a TD

videos.headline: Kentucky recovers Tennessee muffed punt return
videos.description: Grant McKinniss punt for 47-yards , Josh Smith returns for 8-yards to the Tenn 36 Josh Smith fumbled, recovered by Kent Kynan Smith

videos.headline: Jojo Kemp wins the footrace for the 71-yard score
videos.description: Jojo Kemp takes the handoff and runs away from the Tennessee defense for the 71-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Dobbs runs 45 yards for 5th score of the day
videos.description: Tennessee's Joshua Dobbs rushes 45 yards for a fourth-quarter touchdown against Kentucky.

videos.headline: Kamara shrugs off the Kentucky D for TD run
videos.description: Alvin Kamara run for 29-yards for a TD

videos.headline: Kentucky OL provides the extra push as King goes 24-yards to the house
videos.description: Sihiem King run for 24-yards for a TD (Austin MacGinnis KICK)

videos.headline: Austin MacGinnis lays down pitch perfect on-side kick, Kentucky recovers
videos.description: Austin MacGinnis on-side kick recovered by KENTUCKY at the Kent 47

videos.headline: Johnson does it himself on the 2-yard run
videos.description: Stephen Johnson run for 2-yards for a TD (Austin MacGinnis KICK)
